story.title: My Fiance's Brother - Episode 1
story.storyDescription: Taylor is marrying her best friend's brother. But then her best friend confesses he's in love with her...
story.creator: web-uploader

author.bio: Cecy Robson writing as Rosalina San Tiago is an author of contemporary romance, young adult adventure, and award-winning urban fantasy.

messages.text: You just told me you‚Äôre in love with me.
Two days before I marry YOUR BROTHER!
Maybe you should marry me instead.
Don‚Äôt you think I‚Äôve tried to ignore what I feel?
All those times you kissed my brother‚Ä¶
God, do you know what it did to me?
WTF? We‚Äôve known each other forever.
And you‚Äôre telling me this now?
I know this is bad timing.
But he‚Äôs not the right man.
Tay, he‚Äôs been cheating on you for years.
No, you have to believe me.
Remember that night you called me, crying?
The night Blake claimed he had to work late?
You cooked an entire dinner for him.
YOU KNEW he was cheating that night.
With a new client he was trying to impress.
Then why didn‚Äôt he tell you ahead of time?
Why did it take you calling him out?
I shouldn‚Äôt have told you about that night.
I shouldn‚Äôt have called you crying.
You always call me when you‚Äôre sad.
Why do you think that is?
Because you‚Äôre easy to talk to.
You‚Äôve always been here for me.
Wow, how is possible you always make me laugh‚Ä¶even in moments like this?
C‚Äômon. You know I‚Äôm hot. My guess? It‚Äôs the tats.
Don‚Äôt tell me you don‚Äôt like my tats.
Of course I do! I was there every time you got inked.
My tat of the skull with a rose clenched between her teeth?
Hey, don‚Äôt be casting shade on Melinda.
You there? I know you‚Äôre laughing üòâ
Maybe I am‚Ä¶but I don‚Äôt want to.
How long has he been with this woman?
It can if it‚Äôs more than one woman.
It‚Äôs never been the same woman twice.
You have to be kidding me!
You shouldn‚Äôt ‚Äî Blake doesn‚Äôt do it to hurt you.
He does it because deep down, he knows you‚Äôre not the one for him.
Just like you know he‚Äôs not the one for you.
If you marry Blake, you‚Äôll have to give up teaching music and stay home.
Maybe I want to stay home and be responsible.
I mean, damn, you jump out of planes for fun.
That was one time. Okay, twice‚Äî
Did I dare you to run barefoot through park?
We were both drunk and you were barefoot, too.
Only because you threw my shoes in the lake!
That was a total accident. And you weren‚Äôt drunk when you railed on that guy at the zoo.
That GUY was mean to the monkeys.
And you weren‚Äôt drunk when you marched in that protest.
If we don‚Äôt save the elephants, no one will.
True. We can‚Äôt forget the elephants.
Thanks for making me chase my dreams.
My parents always believed in Blake.
I was always in detention for fighting.
Don‚Äôt you remember me and Bill Hicks going at it?
I remember you pounding Bill for hitting his girlfriend.
That‚Äôs not how my parents took it.
No. They were worried about my record.
They wanted me to go to an Ivy League college like Blake.
They didn‚Äôt want me to be an artist.
They had a different future in mind.
Yeah. The same one as Blake‚Äôs.
No. They didn‚Äôt believe in me.
That can‚Äôt be right. You‚Äôre a gifted artist.
And you‚Äôre a great friend for making me see it.
She is a smart little tat.
It‚Äôs all I‚Äôve wanted since Blake brought you home.
The first time? Right before prom?
Even Melinda and she hates everyone.
You tried to get to know me.
None of Blake‚Äôs girlfriends ever did.
It is. Those prissy girls saw a tattooed punk with a black Mohawk.
You would have figured it out.
Or someone else would have seen it.
No, us talking like we‚Äôre more than friends.
But you kissed my soul when it was broken.
And I kissed your heart each time it shattered.
Because of a lot of things.
You‚Äôre the best man at our wedding.
I know. I just wish I was yours.
In a lot of ways you are.
Remember how Blake freaked out when I cut my hair?
He likes it long and blond.
Then why didn‚Äôt you stop me?
Why did you hand me the scissors?
It was going to a little girl with cancer who needed it more.
What am I going to do with you?
IDK, maybe give us a chance?
I have to go through with the wedding.
